ERROR:ASSIGN_IN_IF: do not use assignment in if condition
#143: FILE: sound/drivers/opl3/opl3_seq.c:244:
+	if ((err = snd_opl3_synth_create_port(opl3)) < 0) {

Do not use assignments in if condition.
Example::

  if ((foo = bar(...)) < BAZ) {

should be written as::

  foo = bar(...);
  if (foo < BAZ) {

